{
  "stem": "268.9",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So it was a puppy love, yet a deep love, because the circumstances under which this relationship developed forced us to grow up all of a sudden from-- from-- There was no puppy.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was no adolescence in between, you see.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So yes, I did have a good mental picture, but no actual pictures of her.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So this, again, returning to August 1945, my cousin, who then-- she survived, and I thought, she can live with us.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had a big four room apartment, so she had her own place.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she went to shop, to the marketplace.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there was also a stop-- a tram would stop, would be the end station.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And she was shopping at a marketplace.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Some people got off the street car.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And one of them approached my cousin Regina, and would tell her in Polish, excuse me, please, would you know of any Jewish people living here in this town?",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And my cousin Regina would say, yes, a few.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But why are you asking me?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And Jews in Poland would somehow recognize one another.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There was something in your eyes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And if you-- if you didn't have a word like, say, [HEBREW], which means-- it's a Hebrew word.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know how it was adopted in-- in Ashkenazi.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But one word, [HEBREW], and if-- and if you answered positively, then of course, you were one of the tribe.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this was almost like a password.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so she would ask her, why are you asking me if I know any Jewish people?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So this girl who got off the street car, kind of skinny, short cut hair, undernourished-- she could hardly walk, weak-- says, well, because I thought you might be Jewish.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She says, well, as a matter of fact, yes, I am Jewish.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
